queries.sql: SELECT `partner_lead`.*, CASE WHEN partner_lead.is_view = 1 THEN enquiry_lead.email ELSE 'xxxxx' END AS email, CASE WHEN partner_lead.is_view = 1 THEN enquiry_lead.phone ELSE 'xxxxx' END AS phone, `enquiry_lead`.`name` as `name`, `enquiry_lead`.`message` as `message`, `enquiry_lead`.`service_name` as `service_name`, `states`.`name` as `state_name`, `users`.`image` as `image` FROM `partner_lead` LEFT JOIN `enquiry_lead` ON `enquiry_lead`.`id` = `partner_lead`.`lead_id` LEFT JOIN `service` ON `service`.`id` = `enquiry_lead`.`service_id` LEFT JOIN `states` ON `states`.`id` = `enquiry_lead`.`state` LEFT JOIN `users` ON `users`.`id` = `enquiry_lead`.`user_id` WHERE `partner_lead`.`status` = 1 AND `partner_lead`.`partner_id` = '17' ORDER BY `partner_lead`.`id` DESC LIMIT 12
